{"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-211-Bonjour-Network-Discovery-and-Connectivity"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"title":"Bonjour Network Discovery and Connectivity","role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"WWDC11"},"abstract":[{"text":"Bonjour, also known as zero-configuration networking, enables automatic discovery of computers, devices, and services on IP networks. A wide range of Apple’s products-from iMacs and MacBooks to AirPort Base Stations and Time Capsules, Apple TVs to iPhones, iPod touches and iPads-use Bonjour for streamlined and reliable networking. Learn how to use Bonjour to make it easy for your applications to publish, discover, and resolve network services.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference","isActive":true}]}]}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/211\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}},"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-211-bonjour-network-discovery-and-connectivity"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"references":{"WWDC11-Icon.png":{"type":"image","alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNo